{"id":4359,"date":"2024-01-03T04:06:29","date_gmt":"2020-01-02T22:36:29","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=4359"},"modified":"2024-11-11T16:22:21","modified_gmt":"2024-11-11T10:52:21","slug":"almirah-designs-for-indian-bedroom","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/almirah-designs-for-indian-bedroom\/","title":{"rendered":"Make Your Chamber Impressive With These Almirah Designs For Indian Bedrooms"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>Create an outstanding chamber with these modern almirah designs for your bedroom.<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Almirahs are free-standing <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/wardrobe-design\/\">wardrobes<\/a> that lets you store and locate all your valuables. Essentially, in Indian households, almirahs are placed in bedrooms to place clothes, jewelry, and precious collectibles.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Most homeowners tend to think of almirahs as purely functional pieces of furniture in reality they significantly impact the interior design of your bedroom. Be it a palatial bedroom or a modest one, almirahs cannot be ignored. Essentially, you should not compromise with the style and scheme of almirah for these very reasons.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>With minimal attention to colours, materials, textures, and scale you can create stunning almirah designs for small bedrooms as well.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here&#8217;s presenting our handpicked designs for stunning bedroom almirahs that you can refer to for that much-needed bedroom overhaul.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"608\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/28095657\/almirah-designs-for-indian-bedroom-1-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"Almirah Designs For Indian Bedrooms\" class=\"wp-image-44912\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/28095657\/almirah-designs-for-indian-bedroom-1-scaled.jpg 608w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/28095657\/almirah-designs-for-indian-bedroom-1-71x300.jpg 71w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/28095657\/almirah-designs-for-indian-bedroom-1-243x1024.jpg 243w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/28095657\/almirah-designs-for-indian-bedroom-1-768x3232.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/28095657\/almirah-designs-for-indian-bedroom-1-365x1536.jpg 365w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/28095657\/almirah-designs-for-indian-bedroom-1-150x631.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Wall Almirah Designs For Bedrooms<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The walls around your bed often overlooked. You can judiciously use the wall behind your bed by building an almirah around it.&nbsp; This works for both small or large bedrooms. Your walls can be utilised well with the right almirah design. Opt for subtle colours for almirahs to make your bedroom look minimal and classy.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21000835\/wall-almirah-designs-for-bedroom-indian.jpg\" alt=\"Almirah design by the walls around the bed in a subtle colour for small or large bedrooms\" class=\"wp-image-4360\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21000835\/wall-almirah-designs-for-bedroom-indian.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21000835\/wall-almirah-designs-for-bedroom-indian-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21000835\/wall-almirah-designs-for-bedroom-indian-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21000835\/wall-almirah-designs-for-bedroom-indian-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">An almirah by the walls around the bed makes great use of space<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Upgrade your lifestyle with functional modular wardrobes\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/15145353\/upgrade-your-lifestyle-with-functional-modular-wardrobes.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Sliding Almirah Designs For Bedroom<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Modern almirah designs for bedrooms are built with smart features like sliding doors to make smart use of space. Almirahs not only occupies floor space but also occupies vertical space when you open its doors. Therefore, it makes perfect sense to use a sliding door for almirah. This way you can save space without compromising on modern functionalities and design trends.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21000838\/sliding-almirah-designs-for-indian-bedroom.jpg\" alt=\"Sliding almirah design for bedroom to make smart use of space\" class=\"wp-image-4361\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21000838\/sliding-almirah-designs-for-indian-bedroom.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21000838\/sliding-almirah-designs-for-indian-bedroom-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21000838\/sliding-almirah-designs-for-indian-bedroom-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21000838\/sliding-almirah-designs-for-indian-bedroom-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Save space in your bedroom by opting for almirah with sliding doors<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, check out <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/sliding-wardrobe-design-ideas\/\">Sliding Wardrobe Design Ideas in 2020<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Wooden Almirah Designs For Bedrooms<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Wood is one of the most versatile materials that you can use for your bedroom almirah. With umpteen patterns and textures available in the market these days, wooden almirahs lend a soothing vibe to your bedroom. It is also a great way to inculcate a modern yet classic look to your chamber.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21000843\/wooden-almirah-designs-for-bedroom.jpg\" alt=\"Wooden almirah design for bedroom with umpteen patterns and textures available in the market\" class=\"wp-image-4362\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21000843\/wooden-almirah-designs-for-bedroom.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21000843\/wooden-almirah-designs-for-bedroom-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21000843\/wooden-almirah-designs-for-bedroom-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21000843\/wooden-almirah-designs-for-bedroom-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Wooden almirahs are modern and minimal in their look and feel<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p> Also, check out <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/wooden-wardrobe-design-ideas\/\">Wooden Wardrobe Designs For Bedroom<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Almirah Design For Bedroom With A Mirror<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Are you in a dilemma about where to place a mirror in your bedroom? Well your almirah has all the answers! Let one door of your almirah be covered in mirror &#8211; it is one of the oldest design tricks and still in trend. This not only saves you space but since mirrors reflect light it will make your bedroom look more spacious. Overall, mirrors also makes your wardrobe look sleeker and more streamlined. Make the most use of it!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21000846\/bedroom-almari-design-with-mirror.jpg\" alt=\"Almirah designs with a mirror for bedroom for a sleeker and streamlined look\" class=\"wp-image-4363\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21000846\/bedroom-almari-design-with-mirror.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21000846\/bedroom-almari-design-with-mirror-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21000846\/bedroom-almari-design-with-mirror-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21000846\/bedroom-almari-design-with-mirror-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Almirah with mirrors are perfect for small bedrooms as it make a room appear spacious<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Sunmica For Bedroom Almirah Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Though sunmica is known to be a conventional material, if used smartly it can transform the look and feel of your almirah. And more than that, decor-wise, it can up the ante of your bedroom. Choose a simple combination of colour and textured sunmica to play with and then take a backseat and watch how wonderful your new and improved bedroom will look.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21000850\/sunmica-design-for-bedroom-almirah.jpg\" alt=\"Sunmica Almirah designs for bedroom to transform the look and feel of the space\" class=\"wp-image-4364\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21000850\/sunmica-design-for-bedroom-almirah.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21000850\/sunmica-design-for-bedroom-almirah-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21000850\/sunmica-design-for-bedroom-almirah-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21000850\/sunmica-design-for-bedroom-almirah-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Sunmica is a great material to use for bedroom almirahs<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Ceiling To Floor Almirahs Make Good Use of Space<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Ceiling to floor almirahs are a quintessentially modern design for bedrooms. This design makes the most of every inch in your bedroom and gives you lots more storage to stack away everything you need without clutter. This almirah design is perfect for small rooms.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21000854\/ceiling-floor-almirahs-design-indian-bedroom.jpg\" alt=\"Ceiling to floor Almirah designs for bedroom to transform the look and feel of the space\" class=\"wp-image-4365\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21000854\/ceiling-floor-almirahs-design-indian-bedroom.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21000854\/ceiling-floor-almirahs-design-indian-bedroom-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21000854\/ceiling-floor-almirahs-design-indian-bedroom-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21000854\/ceiling-floor-almirahs-design-indian-bedroom-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Make the most of extra space in your small room with a ceiling to floor almirah<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Peek-A-Boo Almirah Design For Your Bedroom<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Translucent wardrobes are quite in trend these days. It is a stately way to revamp your almirah design as it lets you show off your clothing and accessories. At the same time translucent shutters&nbsp; make your <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/bedroom-design\/\">bedroom interiors<\/a> look trendy and elegant.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21000858\/translucent-wardrobes-almirah-design-for-bedroom.jpg\" alt=\"Peek-a-boo Almirah designs for bedroom which are translucent and quite trendy\" class=\"wp-image-4366\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21000858\/translucent-wardrobes-almirah-design-for-bedroom.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21000858\/translucent-wardrobes-almirah-design-for-bedroom-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21000858\/translucent-wardrobes-almirah-design-for-bedroom-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21000858\/translucent-wardrobes-almirah-design-for-bedroom-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Translucent almirah shutters make this bedroom classy<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Almirah Design In Sync With Bedroom Interiors<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Good almirah design is always aligned with the colour palette of your bedroom interiors. So the colour scheme of your bed, flooring and almirah need to be in the same plane. For instance, if your bedroom floor is grey then design an almirah in the same shade or mix and match with its variants.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21000901\/befitting-almirah-for-bedroom-interiors.jpg\" alt=\"Almirah designs which are in sync with the overall colour pallette of the bedroom interiors\" class=\"wp-image-4367\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21000901\/befitting-almirah-for-bedroom-interiors.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21000901\/befitting-almirah-for-bedroom-interiors-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21000901\/befitting-almirah-for-bedroom-interiors-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21000901\/befitting-almirah-for-bedroom-interiors-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A befitting almirah for your bedroom stays in sync with the overall colour palette of the space<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Create Almirah With Subtle Colours and Textures<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Whenever you choose a darker palette, your room automatically looks dingier and claustrophobic. Hence, choose a subtle texture and lighter colour palette for your almirah and your bedroom will look larger.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21000904\/colours-textures-for-indian-bedroom-almirah-designs.jpg\" alt=\"Almirah designs in subtle colours and textures so that your bedroom looks larger\" class=\"wp-image-4368\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21000904\/colours-textures-for-indian-bedroom-almirah-designs.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21000904\/colours-textures-for-indian-bedroom-almirah-designs-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21000904\/colours-textures-for-indian-bedroom-almirah-designs-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21000904\/colours-textures-for-indian-bedroom-almirah-designs-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A combination of light colours for your almirah makes your room look spacious<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Now that you are on top of best almirah designs for your bedroom, rethink your space to create a grand impression. If you need any further help to do so, do not hesitate to meet our&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\">best interior designers in bangalore<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Explore, More About<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/modern-wardrobe-designs-for-bedroom\/\">Modern Wardrobe Designs For Bedroom<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/wall-fixing-almirah-ideas\/\">Wall-Fixing Almirah Ideas<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/wardrobe-laminate-design\/\">Wardrobe Laminate Design Ideas<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/small-almirah-designs\/\">Stunning Small Almirah Design Ideas<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offse